321
00:15:56,832 --> 00:15:58,666
My head is full of wrong ideas.

322
00:15:58,792 --> 00:16:02,628
You have such
great taste, Claire.
Thank you.

323
00:16:02,712 --> 00:16:05,589
I remember Phil used to have
really good taste too.

324
00:16:05,715 --> 00:16:07,591
Let me get a little of this.
Oh, here it is.

325
00:16:07,717 --> 00:16:09,844
Phil, would you mind grabbing
us a couple glasses?
You betcha.

