337
00:16:39,624 --> 00:16:42,251
- Now I don't know!
- [Claire] Phil?

338
00:16:45,088 --> 00:16:48,340
Phil, honey.
[Running]

339
00:16:48,425 --> 00:16:51,510
Do you remember
when you broke your arm
when we were first dating?

340
00:16:51,595 --> 00:16:53,512
Yeah, uh, when I slipped
on the ice.

341
00:16:53,597 --> 00:16:55,764
Right. That's so weird.
Because in this picture,

342
00:16:55,849 --> 00:16:58,726
you're sitting with Denise
and you have a broken arm, so-

343
00:16:58,810 --> 00:17:00,811
Yeah, that's- that's weird.

344
00:17:00,896 --> 00:17:03,939
- So you were still dating her
when you started dating me?
- No.

345
00:17:04,024 --> 00:17:05,733
- Phil?
- Yeah. Maybe.

346
00:17:05,817 --> 00:17:07,735
There was a time, a little overlap...

347
00:17:07,819 --> 00:17:09,820
when, uh, I was trying
to break things off with Denise.

348
00:17:09,905 --> 00:17:11,822
Uh-huh.
You took me
to Santa Fe.

349
00:17:11,907 --> 00:17:15,534
Santa Fe?
Phil, you told me
that was your father.

