00:17:15,619 --> 00:17:18,204
Okay, I know the pain is fresh,
but the lie is really old.

351
00:17:18,288 --> 00:17:22,041
You know, this was a mistake.
I'm gonna leave.

352
00:17:22,125 --> 00:17:24,835
Claire, if I were you,
I would kick him out.

353
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:28,380
Maybe he'd appreciate you more
after he spent a lonely night
in a hotel.

354
00:17:28,465 --> 00:17:30,758
At the Radisson,
by the airport.

355
00:17:30,842 --> 00:17:33,219
[Door Opens, Closes]

356
00:17:33,345 --> 00:17:35,721
You quit?
Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.
It was amazing.

357
00:17:35,805 --> 00:17:37,431
No, no.
This is the new me, Cam.

358
00:17:37,515 --> 00:17:40,142
I am not letting people
run my life anymore.

359
00:17:40,227 --> 00:17:42,686
