360
00:17:42,771 --> 00:17:45,064
Yes! It's exciting!
It's exciting.

361
00:17:45,148 --> 00:17:48,108
Because you followed your heart,
and that is worth celebrating.

362
00:17:48,193 --> 00:17:50,069
Cam, I just feel-
[Laughs]

363
00:17:50,153 --> 00:17:53,197
So liberated.

364
00:17:53,281 --> 00:17:56,033
- Hey.
- And I'm not picking it up.

365
00:17:56,117 --> 00:17:58,285
- Ooh! I like this guy.
